cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC 

The paper discusses recent developments in data collection for grasping and manipulation in robotics, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also mentions the importance of quality datasets in computer vision (cs.CV) and the use of machine learning techniques (cs.AI, cs.LG) in grasping and manipulation. Additionally, the panel discussion touches on the human-robot interaction (cs.HC) aspect of grasping and manipulation.
